Show HN: Silly Face Builder Toy
text:
I created a simple app for my kids and myself to have a little fun. It's a single screen Android app, free, no ads, no account.

- Tap buttons (multiple times) to select brush for features like eye, nose, ear. - Tap canvas to paint. - Stack brushes for new features. Like painting round-nose with normal-nose, will get you a new rounded-nose-with-spots. It's a bit like the alchemy game.

Created with React Native. I want to try to keep everything without language, so it can be a global app out of the box :).

Was just published yesterday, and there will be an update soon where for instance mouth icons can merge to one wide mouth.
